# Title: Uncommon Svchost Parent Process
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2017-08-15
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects an uncommon svchost parent process
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1036.005
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_svchost_uncommon_parent_process.yml

Image="*\\svchost.exe" NOT (ParentImage IN ("*\\Mrt.exe", "*\\MsMpEng.exe", "*\\ngen.exe", "*\\rpcnet.exe", "*\\services.exe", "*\\TiWorker.exe") OR ParentImage IN ("-", "") OR NOT ParentImage=*)